the classical setting, then there is an\noracle-efficient, no-regret algorithm for contextual bandits in the case that\ncontexts arrive in a smooth manner.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 19:22:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 09:36:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 14:35:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
