d at all. A distinct\ndifferentiation between SiO and HNCO has been revealed in our observations and\nthe further analysis of the gas properties traced by both species, which\nconfirms the results from previous chemical modelings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Feb 2022 13:04:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
